data.description: Don’t wait for a new construction when this home is turnkey and built in 2023! Sitting on a premium lot this home features upgrades such as vaulted ceilings throughout the living areas, bay window in the master bedroom, soaking garden tub, open floor plan, and extra insulation wrapped around the home! Call today for a private showing or ask about how you can ASSUME THE SELLER’S INTEREST RATE OF 5.25%!
